summary: Completed comprehensive testing of EstadísticaMente Nivel Superior (university level) module. All backend APIs pass (16/16 tests). Frontend UI testing shows all major features working correctly including Dashboard Superior, Proyectos Superior (4 example projects), Análisis Superior (expandable sections), Actividades Interactivas (5 activities), Profe Marce Superior chat, and Reportes IA Superior.
critical_code_review_comments: Fixed bug in deepseek_service.py line 170 - incorrect f-string syntax {{}} in .get() default value causing 'unhashable type: dict' error when generating reports for superior level
ESLint warnings in frontend about missing useEffect dependencies (GraficosSuperior.js, CargaDatosSuperior.js, AnalisisSuperior.js) - these are minor and don't affect functionality
Authentication is MOCKED - AuthContext uses localStorage demo user instead of real Firebase auth
seed_data_creation: Example projects for Superior level can be loaded from Proyectos Superior page: Rendimiento Académico Universitario, Salarios en Tecnología, Clima y Rendimiento de Cosecha, Ensayo Clínico - Eficacia de Tratamiento
context_for_next_testing_agent: All Superior level features are working. Backend APIs tested: projects CRUD with superior educationLevel, datasets with multivariate data, chat with educationLevel=superior, reports/generate with education_level=superior. Frontend pages tested: Dashboard Superior, Proyectos Superior (4 example projects), Análisis Superior (7 expandable sections), Actividades Interactivas (5 activities), Profe Marce Superior, Reportes IA Superior. The emerald/teal/cyan color scheme is correctly applied.

features_tested.Proyectos Superior - 4 Example Projects: PASS - Rendimiento Académico (5 vars, 40 records), Salarios Tech (3 vars, 40 records), Clima Cosecha (4 vars, 40 records), Ensayo Clínico (4 vars, 40 records)
features_tested.Crear Nuevo Proyecto Superior: PASS - Dialog opens with analysis types (univariado, multivariado, regresion, inferencia, experimental), redirects to carga datos after creation
features_tested.Cargar Proyecto de Ejemplo: PASS - Successfully loads example project with data and shows success toast
features_tested.Análisis Superior - Expandable Sections: PASS - Tabla de Frecuencias (Simples/Agrupados), Medidas de Posición, Regresión Lineal Simple, Correlación de Pearson, Intervalo de Confianza, Prueba de Hipótesis, Test de Normalidad
features_tested.Actividades Interactivas: PASS - 5 activities: Simulación Teorema Central del Límite, Pruebas de Hipótesis, Estimación de Regresión, Adivinar la Correlación, Intervalos de Confianza
features_tested.Profe Marce Superior: PASS - Chat interface with welcome message mentioning advanced topics (t-test, chi-cuadrado, ANOVA, regresión, correlación, intervalos de confianza, diseño experimental), suggested questions, LaTeX support
features_tested.Reportes IA Superior: PASS - Project selector, Generate Report button, info section explaining academic language, LaTeX formulas, conclusions, limitations discussion
features_tested.Backend /api/chat with educationLevel=su: PASS - Returns detailed responses appropriate for university level
features_tested.Backend /api/reports/generate with educa: PASS - Generates academic reports after bug fix

mocked_apis.AuthContext: Login/logout is mocked using localStorage demo user
